				<p>
					Our Spanish lessons are provided by <a href="http://www.spongeschool.com/" class="section_link">sponge</a>. Classes are taught completely in Spanish by native-speaking teachers. The children engage in developmentally appropriate games and activities and learn through music, movement, drama, and art.
