					<li><span class="schedule">11:30 - 12:00</span> Preschoolers</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					Our preschool class participates in a swim program during the school year (September through May). The class travels off sight to <a href="http://www.seattle.gov/parks/aquatics/meadowbrookpool.htm" class="section_link">Meadowbrook Pool</a>, adjacent to the Meadowbrook Community Center.
				</p>
